lockquote>你條垃圾得把口 夠薑就獨立啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>咪撚轉移視線啦五毛狗<br />\n返去奶你老細鞋底啦廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>死廢物港毒狗得把口 去攞傷殘津貼啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你老母係下面同老毛含緊撚你仲做五毛, 好撚不孝呀你個仆街含撚五毛狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a40609bb9b2bf79acbe299ebbe7f62b2a6456129","tid":538022,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T10:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好奇想知點先可以拎到<br />\n想去美國做二等公民 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"479bea1c8d0901a251aea5124d6f588b868cce76","tid":538022,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T10:07:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>死廢物港毒狗得把口 去攞傷殘津貼啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>外國勢力不得對香港內政說三道四啊<br />\n有冇睇你本五毛手冊啊澳門狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>快d派你支港獨軍打鳩我地啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔打正契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>最好核平澳門啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n洗撚核平咩<br />\n一個颱風你都五勞七傷啦<br />\n笑撚死人咩低賤澳狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}